snippet.title: Wangan Dead Heat + Real Arrange /  湾岸デッドヒート＋リアルアレンジ (Sega Saturn)
snippet.description:
First race in scenario mode from Wangan Dead Heat + Real Arrange for Sega Saturn. released in 1996 by Pack-In-Video and Victor.

OKish I guess... have to play it more. Also note the odd drifting physics.
